Revision history for P5sleep

0.0.5  2018-04-28T09:33:11+02:00
    - simplify sleep return value logic using sleep-timer
    - remove some pod droppings

0.0.4  2018-04-11T16:34:31+02:00
    - Follow App:Mi6's default Changes format

0.0.3  2018-01-31T00:24:03+01:00
    - Resolve the original sleep() at compile time.

0.0.2  2018-01-30T10:50:02+01:00
    - Make sure we respect the Int-ness of sleep() on Perl 5.  Only the
      sleep() exported by Time::Hires knows about fractional sleep times.
      Zoffix++ for pointing that out.

0.0.1  2018-01-30T10:01:01+01:00
    - Initial implementation.
